channel.title: Help please read!
channel.description: Alright everyone thanks for reading. Now so far, I've created a No-Ip account, downloaded No-Ip DUC, created a host and port forwarded. I checked if my ports were forwarded with the port checker tool and they are. Now i'm using my other computer to try and log on, and running the server from this computer. I changed the IP my client connects to in Gui.java. But it doesn't let me connect. What's wrong?? Do I need to restart my computer? Please reply.
